## Icons

- Lead and trail icons allowed in text buttons.
- Icon-only buttons:
  - Same variants + states as text buttons
  - Icon sizes scale with button size:
    - sm = 16px, md = 24px, lg = 28px, xl = 32px
  - Padding must be token-based (`spacing-sm`, `spacing-md`, etc.)
  - Must include `aria-label` for accessibility.

---

## Accessibility

- Minimum 4.5:1 contrast ratio in default and hover states.
- Disabled state must look visually distinct and non-interactive.
- All focus states must remain visible with the semantic focus ring.
- Icon-only buttons must always have `aria-label` or `title`.

